title: Eddie Wants To Walk From West Virginia To Tennessee + Never Gonna Get It: #1 Thing Women Want To Bring Home From Vacation + One Hit Wonder Game!
itunes:title: Eddie Wants To Walk From West Virginia To Tennessee + Never Gonna Get It: #1 Thing Women Want To Bring Home From Vacation + One Hit Wonder Game!
description:
Eddie claims that the journey from West Virginia Down to Tennessee is not that big of an effort to show your love…based on the lyrics of “Carrying Your Love With Me” by George Strait. So we told him to prove it by making the walk himself. He doesn’t want to…but he reveals to us what he needs to follow through. According to a new survey of 2000 women, this is the most important thing to bring home from a vacation. What is it??? In honor of Billy Gilman’s birthday….we play a round of The One Hit Wonder Game!
